properties.property:
return function(self, dt) if not self.scene:playerMovable() or self.stopMoving then return end
local fx = self.scene.player.fx if self.scene.player.noGas or self.nofollow then fx = 25 end
local bx = self.scene.player.bx if bx > 0 then bx = bx + 1 end self.x = self.x + (fx + bx + math.random(-0.5, 0.5)) * (dt/0.016)
if self.followPlayerY then if self.y + self.sprite.h > self.scene.player.y + 10 then self.y = self.y - 2*(dt/0.016) elseif self.y + self.sprite.h < self.scene.player.y - 10 then self.y = self.y + 2*(dt/0.016) end end end
